---
import Layout from '../../../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import PageShell from '../../../../components/PageShell.astro';
import CTABox from '../../../../components/CTABox.astro';
import ComparisonTable from '../../../../components/ComparisonTable.astro';

const title = "St. Lucia Citizenship by Investment Guide 2025";
const description = "Complete guide to St. Lucia's CBI program. $100,000 NEF donation, 145+ countries visa-free, government bonds option, and comprehensive insurance requirements for Caribbean citizenship.";

const schema = {
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": "Article",
  "headline": title,
  "description": description,
  "author": {
    "@type": "Organization",
    "name": "Compare Expat Plans"
  },
  "datePublished": "2025-01-15",
  "dateModified": "2025-01-15"
};
---

<Layout title={title} description={description}>
  <script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify(schema)} />

  <PageShell
    title={title}
    subtitle="Your complete guide to citizenship by investment in St. Lucia"
    heroImage="/images/countries/st-lucia-hero-bg.png"
  >
    <!-- Quick Facts Box -->
    <div class="bg-primary-50 border border-primary-200 rounded-lg p-6 mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-primary-900 mb-4">St. Lucia CBI: Quick Facts</h2>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 text-sm">
        <div>
          <span class="font-semibold text-neutral-700">Minimum Investment:</span>
          <span class="text-neutral-900"> $100,000 NEF donation</span>
        </div>
        <div>
          <span class="font-semibold text-neutral-700">Processing Time:</span>
          <span class="text-neutral-900"> 3-4 months</span>
        </div>
        <div>
          <span class="font-semibold text-neutral-700">Visa-Free Countries:</span>
          <span class="text-neutral-900"> 145+ (including UK, EU, Singapore)</span>
        </div>
        <div>
          <span class="font-semibold text-neutral-700">Residency Requirement:</span>
          <span class="text-neutral-900"> None</span>
        </div>
        <div>
          <span class="font-semibold text-neutral-700">Family Inclusion:</span>
          <span class="text-neutral-900"> Spouse, children, parents, grandparents</span>
        </div>
        <div>
          <span class="font-semibold text-neutral-700">Unique Option:</span>
          <span class="text-neutral-900"> Government bonds (refundable)</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Overview Section -->
    <section id="overview" class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-neutral-900 mb-4">Overview</h2>
      <p class="text-neutral-700 mb-4">
        St. Lucia's Citizenship by Investment Program, launched in 2015, offers one of the Caribbean's most flexible
        CBI options with multiple investment pathways including a unique government bond option. The program provides
        visa-free access to 145+ countries including the UK, Schengen Area, Singapore, and Hong Kong—making it
        attractive for global business travelers and those seeking travel freedom.
      </p>
      <p class="text-neutral-700 mb-4">
        What sets St. Lucia apart is its government bond option—a refundable investment that returns your principal
        after 5 years. While the upfront cost is higher than the donation option, it appeals to investors who prefer
        capital preservation. The program also has no residency requirement whatsoever—you never need to visit
        St. Lucia to obtain or maintain citizenship.
      </p>
      <p class="text-neutral-700 mb-4">
        The island's healthcare system centers on two main hospitals with limited specialist services. For complex
        medical care, evacuation to Barbados, Martinique, or Miami is standard practice. International health insurance
        with evacuation coverage is essential for anyone planning to spend time on the island.
      </p>
    </section>

    <!-- Quick Decision Guide -->
    <section id="decision-guide" class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-neutral-900 mb-4">Quick Decision Guide</h2>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <div class="bg-green-50 border border-green-200 rounded-lg p-6">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-green-800 mb-3">St. Lucia CBI is Ideal If You:</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-green-900">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-600 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
              </svg>
              <span>Want a refundable investment option (government bonds)</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-600 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
              </svg>
              <span>Prefer zero residency requirements (never need to visit)</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-600 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
              </svg>
              <span>Need UK and EU visa-free access</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-600 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
              </svg>
              <span>Are interested in real estate in a tourism-focused economy</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-600 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
              </svg>
              <span>Value a smaller, more boutique CBI program</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-amber-50 border border-amber-200 rounded-lg p-6">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-amber-800 mb-3">Consider Alternatives If You:</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-amber-900">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-amber-600 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M8.257 3.099c.765-1.36 2.722-1.36 3.486 0l5.58 9.92c.75 1.334-.213 2.98-1.742 2.98H4.42c-1.53 0-2.493-1.646-1.743-2.98l5.58-9.92zM11 13a1 1 0 11-2 0 1 1 0 012 0zm-1-8a1 1 0 00-1 1v3a1 1 0 002 0V6a1 1 0 00-1-1z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
              </svg>
              <span>Need US E-2 Treaty access (choose Grenada)</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-amber-600 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M8.257 3.099c.765-1.36 2.722-1.36 3.486 0l5.58 9.92c.75 1.334-.213 2.98-1.742 2.98H4.42c-1.53 0-2.493-1.646-1.743-2.98l5.58-9.92zM11 13a1 1 0 11-2 0 1 1 0 012 0zm-1-8a1 1 0 00-1 1v3a1 1 0 002 0V6a1 1 0 00-1-1z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
              </svg>
              <span>Want absolute lowest cost (Dominica is slightly cheaper)</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-amber-600 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M8.257 3.099c.765-1.36 2.722-1.36 3.486 0l5.58 9.92c.75 1.334-.213 2.98-1.742 2.98H4.42c-1.53 0-2.493-1.646-1.743-2.98l5.58-9.92zM11 13a1 1 0 11-2 0 1 1 0 012 0zm-1-8a1 1 0 00-1 1v3a1 1 0 002 0V6a1 1 0 00-1-1z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
              </svg>
              <span>Prefer the most established program (St. Kitts since 1984)</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-amber-600 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M8.257 3.099c.765-1.36 2.722-1.36 3.486 0l5.58 9.92c.75 1.334-.213 2.98-1.742 2.98H4.42c-1.53 0-2.493-1.646-1.743-2.98l5.58-9.92zM11 13a1 1 0 11-2 0 1 1 0 012 0zm-1-8a1 1 0 00-1 1v3a1 1 0 002 0V6a1 1 0 00-1-1z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
              </svg>
              <span>Need excellent local healthcare (limited specialist care)</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-amber-600 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M8.257 3.099c.765-1.36 2.722-1.36 3.486 0l5.58 9.92c.75 1.334-.213 2.98-1.742 2.98H4.42c-1.53 0-2.493-1.646-1.743-2.98l5.58-9.92zM11 13a1 1 0 11-2 0 1 1 0 012 0zm-1-8a1 1 0 00-1 1v3a1 1 0 002 0V6a1 1 0 00-1-1z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
              </svg>
              <span>Have a large family of 4+ (Antigua may be better value)</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Official Requirements -->
    <section id="requirements" class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-neutral-900 mb-4">Official Requirements</h2>

      <div class="bg-white border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg p-6 mb-6">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-4">Investment Options</h3>

        <div class="space-y-6">
          <div class="border-l-4 border-primary-500 pl-4">
            <h4 class="font-semibold text-neutral-900">Option 1: National Economic Fund (NEF) Donation</h4>
            <p class="text-neutral-700 mt-2">
              Non-refundable contribution to St. Lucia's National Economic Fund supporting national development.
              The most straightforward option with predictable costs.
            </p>
            <ul class="mt-3 space-y-1 text-neutral-600 text-sm">
              <li>• Single applicant: $100,000</li>
              <li>• Applicant + spouse: $140,000</li>
              <li>• Applicant + spouse + up to 2 dependents: $150,000</li>
              <li>• Each additional dependent: $25,000</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="border-l-4 border-green-500 pl-4">
            <h4 class="font-semibold text-neutral-900">Option 2: Government Bonds (Refundable)</h4>
            <p class="text-neutral-700 mt-2">
              Purchase of non-interest-bearing government bonds. Principal is refunded after 5 years—unique among
              Caribbean CBI programs. Higher upfront cost but capital is preserved.
            </p>
            <ul class="mt-3 space-y-1 text-neutral-600 text-sm">
              <li>• Single applicant: $300,000 (refunded after 5 years)</li>
              <li>• Applicant + spouse: $350,000</li>
              <li>• Each additional dependent: $25,000 (added to bond)</li>
              <li>• Administrative fee: $50,000 (non-refundable)</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="border-l-4 border-primary-500 pl-4">
            <h4 class="font-semibold text-neutral-900">Option 3: Real Estate Investment</h4>
            <p class="text-neutral-700 mt-2">
              Purchase of approved real estate. Must be held for minimum 5 years. Property can generate rental
              income and appreciates in value.
            </p>
            <ul class="mt-3 space-y-1 text-neutral-600 text-sm">
              <li>• Minimum investment: $200,000 (approved projects only)</li>
              <li>• Holding period: 5 years minimum</li>
              <li>• Government processing fee: $30,000 (single), $45,000 (family of 4)</li>
              <li>• Property can be resold to future CBI applicants after 5 years</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="border-l-4 border-primary-500 pl-4">
            <h4 class="font-semibold text-neutral-900">Option 4: Enterprise Project</h4>
            <p class="text-neutral-700 mt-2">
              Investment in an approved enterprise project in specified sectors (specialty restaurants, cruise
              ports, marinas, agro-processing, research facilities).
            </p>
            <ul class="mt-3 space-y-1 text-neutral-600 text-sm">
              <li>• Single investor: $3,500,000 minimum</li>
              <li>• Joint investment: $1,000,000 per investor (minimum 2, total $6,000,000)</li>
              <li>• Must create at least 3 permanent jobs</li>
              <li>• Government approval required</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg p-6 mb-6">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-4">Eligibility Criteria</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-3 text-neutral-700">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-primary-600 font-bold">•</span>
            <span><strong>Age:</strong> Main applicant must be 18 years or older</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-primary-600 font-bold">•</span>
            <span><strong>Clean record:</strong> No criminal convictions, not under investigation, no visa refusals to visa-free countries</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-primary-600 font-bold">•</span>
            <span><strong>Good health:</strong> No communicable diseases, health insurance required</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-primary-600 font-bold">•</span>
            <span><strong>Source of funds:</strong> Legitimate and clearly documented</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-primary-600 font-bold">•</span>
            <span><strong>Dependents:</strong> Spouse, children under 25 (or up to 30 if in education), parents/grandparents 55+</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg p-6">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-4">Required Documents</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-neutral-700">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-primary-600 font-bold">1.</span>
            <span>Completed application forms (signed and notarized)</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-primary-600 font-bold">2.</span>
            <span>Certified passport copies (all pages with entries)</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-primary-600 font-bold">3.</span>
            <span>Birth certificate (certified, apostilled, translated if not in English)</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-primary-600 font-bold">4.</span>
            <span>Marriage certificate if applicable (certified and apostilled)</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-primary-600 font-bold">5.</span>
            <span>Police clearance certificate (from all countries of residence past 10 years)</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-primary-600 font-bold">6.</span>
            <span>Medical certificate (HIV test, full physical)</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-primary-600 font-bold">7.</span>
            <span>Professional reference letter</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-primary-600 font-bold">8.</span>
            <span>Bank reference letter</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-primary-600 font-bold">9.</span>
            <span>Proof of address (utility bill, bank statement)</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-primary-600 font-bold">10.</span>
            <span>Source of funds documentation (6-12 months bank statements, employment/business records)</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-primary-600 font-bold">11.</span>
            <span>6 passport-sized photos per applicant</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-primary-600 font-bold">12.</span>
            <span>Health insurance certificate</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Insurance Requirements -->
    <section id="insurance-requirements" class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-neutral-900 mb-4">Insurance Requirements</h2>

      <div class="bg-amber-50 border border-amber-200 rounded-lg p-6 mb-6">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-amber-800 mb-2">Health Insurance Required</h3>
        <p class="text-amber-900">
          St. Lucia requires proof of valid health insurance as part of the CBI application. The insurance must
          provide coverage in St. Lucia. While minimum coverage amounts aren't specified, comprehensive international
          health insurance with medical evacuation is strongly recommended given the island's limited healthcare facilities.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-6">
        <div class="bg-white border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg p-6">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-3">Recommended Coverage</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-neutral-700">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-600 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
              </svg>
              <span>Annual maximum: $500,000+ recommended</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-600 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
              </svg>
              <span>Medical evacuation (essential)</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-600 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
              </svg>
              <span>Caribbean region coverage</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-600 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
              </svg>
              <span>Certificate valid for application submission</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg p-6">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-3">Why Evacuation is Critical</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-neutral-700">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-red-600 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M8.257 3.099c.765-1.36 2.722-1.36 3.486 0l5.58 9.92c.75 1.334-.213 2.98-1.742 2.98H4.42c-1.53 0-2.493-1.646-1.743-2.98l5.58-9.92zM11 13a1 1 0 11-2 0 1 1 0 012 0zm-1-8a1 1 0 00-1 1v3a1 1 0 002 0V6a1 1 0 00-1-1z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
              </svg>
              <span>Two main hospitals with basic services</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-red-600 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M8.257 3.099c.765-1.36 2.722-1.36 3.486 0l5.58 9.92c.75 1.334-.213 2.98-1.742 2.98H4.42c-1.53 0-2.493-1.646-1.743-2.98l5.58-9.92zM11 13a1 1 0 11-2 0 1 1 0 012 0zm-1-8a1 1 0 00-1 1v3a1 1 0 002 0V6a1 1 0 00-1-1z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
              </svg>
              <span>Limited specialist care on island</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-red-600 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M8.257 3.099c.765-1.36 2.722-1.36 3.486 0l5.58 9.92c.75 1.334-.213 2.98-1.742 2.98H4.42c-1.53 0-2.493-1.646-1.743-2.98l5.58-9.92zM11 13a1 1 0 11-2 0 1 1 0 012 0zm-1-8a1 1 0 00-1 1v3a1 1 0 002 0V6a1 1 0 00-1-1z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
              </svg>
              <span>Martinique evacuation: 30 minutes flight</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-red-600 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M8.257 3.099c.765-1.36 2.722-1.36 3.486 0l5.58 9.92c.75 1.334-.213 2.98-1.742 2.98H4.42c-1.53 0-2.493-1.646-1.743-2.98l5.58-9.92zM11 13a1 1 0 11-2 0 1 1 0 012 0zm-1-8a1 1 0 00-1 1v3a1 1 0 002 0V6a1 1 0 00-1-1z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
              </svg>
              <span>Air ambulance costs $15,000-$40,000+</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-blue-50 border border-blue-200 rounded-lg p-6">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-blue-800 mb-2">Insurance Strategy for CBI Applicants</h3>
        <p class="text-blue-900 mb-4">
          Most St. Lucia CBI holders don't actually live on the island—they use the passport for travel while
          residing elsewhere. Your insurance strategy should match your actual situation:
        </p>
